## ğŸ” Project Overview

This project is a real-time embedded system designed to monitor health parameters such as heart rate, temperature, and SpOâ‚‚, and also detect vehicle accidents using motion sensors. It sends live health stats to the **Blynk** mobile dashboard and triggers emergency alerts via **Telegram Bot**, including location sharing.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ“¡ **Health Monitoring (ESP32 + MAX30105)**  
  - Heart rate detection  
  - Body temperature monitoring  
  - SpOâ‚‚ (blood oxygen level) estimation  

- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Accident Detection (ESP8266 + MPU6050 + GPS)**  
  - Detects abrupt motion indicating an accident  
  - Shares GPS location via Telegram  
  - SOS button for manual emergency alerts  

- ğŸ“² **Real-time Notifications**
  - Blynk app dashboard shows live health data  
  - Telegram bot sends accident alerts and location  

